strings:
<voice_0x0100109F><se_def>Tom: ...Whaaat!?
Master Felix asked you a favour!?

<voice_0x010010A0><se_def>Tom: He must think you're the cat's pyjamas if he
gave you the go-ahead to ride on one of his
great sabrecats!
<voice_0x010010A1><se_def>Tom: Grrrreat! I was right to let you in!
<voice_0x010010A2><se_def>Tom: I could tell you were a hip-cat! Okay!
<voice_0x010010A3><se_def>Tom: So are you ready to get on?
<voice_0x010010A4><se_def>Tom: Eh? Ah, come on! Don't be a scaredy cat, bru!
<voice_0x010010A5><se_def>Tom: Just be brave and everything will be fine!
<voice_0x010010A6><se_def>Tom: That's it! No pain, no gain!
<voice_0x010010A8><se_def>Tom: Okay, let me tell you the basics about riding a great sabrecat.
<voice_0x010010A9><se_def>Tom: When you're riding one of these cats, you can go a lot quicker than you would on foot...
<voice_0x010010AA><se_def>Tom: But you can't go further. You can just go to all the same places faster. Some people get that wrong, so I wanted to explain.
<voice_0x010010AB><se_def>Tom: If you get off and accidentally lose your cat, come back and see me. I'll lend you a cat as many times as you like.

<voice_0x010010AC><se_def>Tom: That's it!
You're ready to go!
Good luck!
